        dc:description           "FIG. 3. — Dental remains of Bulgarian Mephitidae: A-C, Promephitis majori Pilgrim, 1933 (HD-9505); A, 3D model of left I1–M1 in occlusal view (stereo pair A1- A2); B, 3D model of left p4-m2 in occlusal view (stereo pair B1-B2); C, 3D model of right i1-p3 in occlusal view (stereo pair C1-C2); D, Promephitis lartetii Gaudry, 1861 (HD-9507), right P4-M1 (stereo pair D1-D2). Scale bar: 2 cm." ;
